com.ibm.team.build.common.model

Interface IBuildRequestParams


  • public interface IBuildRequestParams
    Represents the parameters to the request build operation.

    The parameters may specify build properties that should be deleted from the requested build as well as new or modified properties. Should a property be present in both lists, the deletion list will take priority and the build property will be deleted.

    Since:
    0.8
